are just as much as mine, if not more.

286
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:07,100
You're already so tired,

287
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:08,260
how could I bear

288
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,100
to let you go out and work too?

289
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:11,500
Actually,

290
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:15,220
I'm doing this for myself.

291
00:13:17,060 --> 00:13:18,620
Didn't we agree

292
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:21,460
that I'd take these three years off to rest,

293
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:23,660
to take care of you and Ziyuan?

294
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:26,940
Now that Ziyuan is in kindergarten,

295
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:29,420
and your company is on track,

296
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:32,900
I think it's time for me to pursue my own career again.

297
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:33,740
What do you think?

298
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:36,900
You don't know

299
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,540
how competitive the workplace is these days.

300
00:13:39,170 --> 00:13:41,140
I'm really worried you'll get too stressed out

301
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:42,980
and relapse.

302
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:46,300
It won't.

303
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,380
The symptoms of my depression

304
00:13:48,380 --> 00:13:50,300
haven't appeared in a long time.

305
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:52,220
Don't worry.

306
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:53,700
I'm fine now.

307
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:56,660
I really want to return to the workforce.

308
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,500
Can you understand that?

309
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:02,940
But aren't you already working at the non-profit service station?

310
00:14:03,820 --> 00:14:06,700
The work there is meaningful,

311
00:14:07,460 --> 00:14:09,500
and it's helped me get back into a better state.

312
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:12,660
But it's different from what I truly want.

313
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,580
I still miss

314
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:17,580
the busy, fast-paced days

315
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:18,860
at the law firm.

316
00:14:19,700 --> 00:14:21,700
That's the stage I've always aspired to be on.

317
00:14:23,740 --> 00:14:24,580
Honey,

318
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:27,020
support me,

319
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:28,380
okay?

320
00:14:31,220 --> 00:14:32,060
Alright, alright.

321
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:33,940
I support you.

322
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:37,180
I fully, completely support you.

323
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:38,580
The two of us,

324
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:40,540
we respect and understand each other.

325
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,260
Thank you, honey.

326
00:15:19,140 --> 00:15:20,480
Mr. Zhang, it's Ning Yue.

327
00:15:20,620 --> 00:15:22,060
Yes, yes, I've reviewed the contract,

328
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:23,020
There's no problem with it.

329
00:15:23,390 --> 00:15:25,660
If the timing works out,

330
00:15:27,230 --> 00:15:28,690
I can start next month.

331
00:15:29,740 --> 00:15:31,100
- Yes.
- Ning.

332
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,100
I'll confirm with you later, okay?

333
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:36,300
Thanks.

334
00:15:36,420 --> 00:15:37,460
You're quitting?

335
00:15:38,100 --> 00:15:39,500
Xia, I just wanted

336
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,620
to discuss something with you.

337
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:42,700
I'm not quitting.

338
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:43,980
I'll still come back on weekends.

339
00:15:43,980 --> 00:15:45,500
You know, we have more jobs to do on weekends.

340
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:46,780
it won't cause any trouble.

341
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:48,100
Ning,

342
00:15:48,340 --> 00:15:49,780
please think it over carefully?

343
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,620
We really can't do this without you.

344
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:53,460
You're the backbone of the team!

345
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:54,460
You don't know

346
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:56,060
how important you are to us.

347
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:57,780
Alright, Xia, I understand.

348
00:15:57,780 --> 00:15:58,700
I'll handle it.

349
00:15:58,860 --> 00:15:59,700
(My wife is at home today.)

350
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:02,700
(Don't worry about saving money for me. What's mine is yours.)
He only gives me 3,000 yuan per month,

351
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,220
but he's willing to buy that woman a random purse

352
00:16:05,220 --> 00:16:06,390
that costs thirty to forty thousand.

353
00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:08,580
(Legal Consultation)
Here's the evidence.

354
00:16:08,580 --> 00:16:09,700
I've sent everything over to you.

355
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:11,340
Got it.

356
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:13,780
Can we still

357
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:15,800
get back these tens of thousands?

358
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,340
Yes, we can recover it.

359
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:20,420
It can be done through unilateral gifts from joint assets,

360
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:21,840
and the rights can be limited and reclaimed.

361
00:16:22,740 --> 00:16:23,620
Ms. Ning,

362
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:25,100
please make sure

363
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,980
to keep these pieces of evidence safe.

364
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:28,660
Make sure no one else sees this.

365
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:31,090
I don't want my son to find out

366
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:33,020
what his dad has done.

367
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,100
I'm afraid it'll hurt him.

368
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:38,620
Ms. Ho,

369
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:40,220
among all my clients,

370
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:41,580
ninety percent of them

371
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:43,300
have the same concern as you.

372
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:45,340
But I have to tell you,

373
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:47,220
once you take this step,

374
00:16:48,010 --> 00:16:49,120
your child will be affected,

375
00:16:49,530 --> 00:16:51,650
even if just a little.

376
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,140
So you need to

377
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:55,940
prepare yourself mentally for that.

378
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:57,940
Don't blame yourself.

379
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:59,140
This isn't your fault.

380
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:01,020
In a marriage,

381
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:03,180
no one can predict that their partner will betray them.

382
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:04,700
Don't worry,

383
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:06,140
Ms. Ho,

384
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:07,420
you'll get through this.

385
00:17:11,860 --> 00:17:13,420
I'll leave this in the hands of you three,

386
00:17:13,430 --> 00:17:14,660
Mr. Guo, Mr. Hu, I'm counting on you.

387
00:17:21,330 --> 00:17:22,170
Have a seat.

388
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,620
Ms. Tian, not bad!

389
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,580
Last time you couldn't even play,

390
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,420
and now you're playing so smoothly.

391
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:36,580
Huge progress!

392
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,020
Crash course.

393
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,020
I only learned this one piece.

394
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:43,420
You're being modest.

395
00:17:48,020 --> 00:17:49,380
Thanks for hosting us!

396
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:50,420
About your matter,

397
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:51,260
leave it to me.

398
00:17:51,370 --> 00:17:52,340
Alright, bye, take care!

399
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:53,180
Bye.

400
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:54,180
Mind your step.

401
00:18:31,980 --> 00:18:33,500
Didn't you say you only learned one piece?

402
00:18:35,900 --> 00:18:37,380
That one was for them.

403
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:42,740
You played it wrong.

404
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:45,500
I did that on purpose.

405
00:18:59,740 --> 00:19:00,620
You lost!

406
00:19:00,980 --> 00:19:01,820
Take a sip of water.

407
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:07,420
Dad,

408
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:09,980
you're a big tree

409
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:11,540
Come on, sit down.

410
00:19:11,740 --> 00:19:13,180
Standing on the chair is dangerous!

411
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,340
that shields the family from storms.

412
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:18,580
What about me?

413
00:19:19,620 --> 00:19:21,620
Mom, you're a little fairy.

414
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:23,980
Such a sweet talker.

415
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:24,820
Son,

416
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:27,180
that's some serious favoritism.

417
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:30,060
I'm not even human now?

418
00:19:31,820 --> 00:19:33,860
Dad, I mean

419
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:36,940
you're like a guardian angel protecting me and Mom!

420
00:19:38,060 --> 00:19:40,220
Honey, you're a guardian angel now.

421
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:41,660
Alright, let me toast to you.

422
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,130
Let's toast.

423
00:19:43,300 --> 00:19:44,540
- Cheers.
- Let me toast you too.

424
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:45,940
Cheers.

425
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:56,180
Honey,

426
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:01,260
it's getting late. Time for bed.

427
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:06,220
How’s your job?

428
00:20:07,020 --> 00:20:09,180
You know, the one you applied for.

429
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:10,460
Don't worry.

430
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:12,380
I've already made everything clear with them.

431
00:20:12,470 --> 00:20:13,900
Next month,

432
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:16,100
I'll officially start working.

433
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:17,940
Let's sleep.

434
00:20:19,340 --> 00:20:20,180
I am tired!

435
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,360
Congcong,

436
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,820
adult matters are hard for kids to understand.

437
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:36,020
Your mom and dad

438
00:20:36,020 --> 00:20:37,300
will take care of their own issues.

439
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:40,580
Come on, have some water.

440
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:44,780
Lawyer Ning will help your mom,

441
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:45,980
trust her.

442
00:20:46,780 --> 00:20:47,620
Yue.

443
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:48,700
Congcong,

444
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:51,340
why are you trying to ruin my parents' relationship?

445
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:58,540
I'm not ruining your parents' relationship.

446
00:20:59,220 --> 00:21:01,180
The adult world is complicated,

447
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:02,940
and there's a lot of things

448
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:04,260
your mom hasn't figured out.

449
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:05,620
How can she explain to you.

450
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:06,900
You're still too young.

451
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:08,540
I know everything.

452
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:09,860
I just know.

453
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:12,260
One of my classmates' parents got divorced.

454
00:21:12,460 --> 00:21:14,380
His dad quickly remarried

455
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:15,650
and completely ignored him after that.

456
00:21:15,900 --> 00:21:16,820
Congcong, but…

457
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:18,620
Do you care about how your mom feels?

458
00:21:19,540 --> 00:21:21,180
Do you care if she's happy?

459
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:22,740
She's happy.

460
00:21:23,420 --> 00:21:25,380
They were fine before.

461
00:21:25,380 --> 00:21:26,980
It's all because of you.

462
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:29,340
You're the one who pushed my mom to get a divorce.

463
00:21:29,580 --> 00:21:30,980
You're not a good person.

464
00:21:31,140 --> 00:21:32,890
You'll get what's coming to you.

465
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,880
Congcong,

466
00:21:33,890 --> 00:21:35,860
Things aren't what you think.

467
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,100
They won't divorce.

468
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:38,500
They're doing this for me.

469
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:39,660
They will NEVER divorce.

470
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:41,180
- Congcong!
- Congcong!

471
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:43,100
Ms. Ning, you're finally back.

472
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:44,540
I need to talk to you about something.

473
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:47,540
Ms. Ning,

474
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:50,180
This is urgent.

475
00:21:53,380 --> 00:21:55,500
I want my mom to come home.

476
00:21:56,180 --> 00:21:57,660
Why is it so noisy downstairs?

477
00:21:58,900 --> 00:22:00,460
Hey, boy, that's dangerous.

478
00:22:10,860 --> 00:22:12,500
I just thought it was noisy downstairs,

479
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:14,540
so I went to the window to take a look.

480
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:16,060
- Please calm down.
- Then,

481
00:22:16,060 --> 00:22:17,700
I saw someone

482
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:20,940
jump down…

483
00:22:22,340 --> 00:22:23,380
Have you seen them

484
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:27,020
before?

485
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:27,940
Did you talk to them?

486
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:29,180
What did they say to you?

487
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:04,380
Why did you post those photos online?

488
00:23:04,780 --> 00:23:05,620
You promised me

489
00:23:05,620 --> 00:23:07,260
you'd keep them safe.

490
00:23:08,180 --> 00:23:09,540
Congcing can't bear it.

491
00:23:09,980 --> 00:23:11,060
How can a son

492
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:13,700
believe his father did something like that?

493
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:15,500
I don't know what you're talking about.

494
00:23:16,460 --> 00:23:18,500
If something happens to my son,

495
00:23:19,180 --> 00:23:20,820
I won't let you get away with it.

496
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:22,740
What's going on?

497
00:23:24,060 --> 00:23:24,900
Honey.

498
00:23:25,340 --> 00:23:27,220
She's hurting my son!

499
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:29,180
The one who did this to your son

500
00:23:30,020 --> 00:23:31,220
is your husband.

501
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:37,860
(One can a day, peaceful sleep every day.)

502
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,180
Honey,

503
00:24:00,180 --> 00:24:01,860
What's going on with these photos?

504
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:04,060
I never posted these photos.

505
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:06,180
Who posted them online?

506
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:09,180
Don't look at them.

507
00:24:09,180 --> 00:24:10,740
No wonder Congcong reacted like that.

508
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:12,380
When I went to the hospital earlier,

509
00:24:12,380 --> 00:24:13,580
his mom kept asking me

510
00:24:13,580 --> 00:24:14,700
why these photos were posted.

511
00:24:14,700 --> 00:24:15,780
Honestly, I didn’t post them.

512
00:24:15,780 --> 00:24:16,820
It wasn’t me.

513
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:18,420
But only I have these photos.

514
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:19,980
I don’t know how they got out.

515
00:24:20,780 --> 00:24:22,220
I asked the doctor,

516
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:24,420
the building wasn't too high.

517
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:26,580
The kid's lucky.

518
00:24:26,780 --> 00:24:28,260
He just has some fractures and bruises,

519
00:24:28,580 --> 00:24:29,420
and probably

520
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:30,780
a concussion,

521
00:24:30,780 --> 00:24:33,100
but no serious lasting damage.

522
00:24:34,780 --> 00:24:35,940
How did you end up at the hospital?

523
00:24:38,020 --> 00:24:39,820
I tried calling you, but you didn't answer.

524
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:41,580
Then I called the service station,

525
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:42,820
and they told me you're at the hospital.

526
00:24:44,860 --> 00:24:46,500
Can you believe it?

527
00:24:47,580 --> 00:24:49,180
This kid has such a temper!

528
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:51,820
Who could’ve expected this?

529
00:25:17,940 --> 00:25:18,780
Honey,

530
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:21,940
you know where the tie is.

531
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:24,260
Thanks to your help,

532
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:25,940
how can I not know.

533
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:30,980
Ziyuan.

534
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:33,420
Dad, I'm coming.

535
00:25:34,100 --> 00:25:35,380
Say goodbye to mom.

536
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:37,180
Bye, Mom.

537
00:25:39,980 --> 00:25:42,060
I'll pick you up in the afternoon, okay?

538
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:43,340
Okay, Mom.

539
00:25:43,420 --> 00:25:44,260
See you in the afternoon.

540
00:25:44,780 --> 00:25:46,020
I'll go pick him up this afternoon.

541
00:25:46,140 --> 00:25:47,540
You rest some more.

542
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:50,020
Alright.

543
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,620
Ziyuan, let's go.

544
00:25:53,230 --> 00:25:55,710
Dad, are you going to send me to school every day,

545
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:56,580
aren't you?

546
00:25:56,580 --> 00:25:57,420
Of course.

547
00:25:58,300 --> 00:26:00,100
(Attorney Ning Yue leaks client's evidence.)

548
00:26:00,100 --> 00:26:02,180
(Pro bono lawyer Ning Yue suspected of leaking client's evidence.)

549
00:26:02,180 --> 00:26:03,900
I contacted the PR team we were discussing cooperation with

550
00:26:03,900 --> 00:26:04,980
