551
00:26:05,620 --> 00:26:07,460
These marketing accounts are truly shameless.

552
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:10,500
Hurry up and fix it.

553
00:26:11,870 --> 00:26:12,710
How's Yue?

554
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,740
Is it hitting her hard?

555
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:17,430
It's my fault.

556
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:18,940
I failed to protect her.

557
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:22,140
How could it be your fault?

558
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:24,450
Actually, back then,

559
00:26:24,450 --> 00:26:25,530
when she wanted to go back to work,

560
00:26:25,540 --> 00:26:27,000
I shouldn't have agreed.

561
00:26:27,730 --> 00:26:28,820
Now it's clear

562
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,500
I was right.

563
00:26:31,620 --> 00:26:32,980
You can't say it like that.

564
00:26:33,780 --> 00:26:35,140
Before Ziyuan was born,

565
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:36,500
she was doing just fine.

566
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:44,420
(Ning Yue)

567
00:26:47,260 --> 00:26:48,220
(Comments)

568
00:26:48,220 --> 00:26:50,700
Some lawyers will do anything for money
