879
00:40:40,980 --> 00:40:42,580
- It looks good.
- Leave it to me.

880
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:43,820
Here.

881
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:45,540
- Let me help.
- Here you are.

882
00:40:45,540 --> 00:40:46,380
You go keep her company.

883
00:40:47,820 --> 00:40:48,660
Add some more oil.

884
00:40:49,580 --> 00:40:50,620
