- Exactly.

885
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:52,740
Honey,

886
00:40:53,540 --> 00:40:55,020
Honey, don't be upset.

887
00:40:56,380 --> 00:40:57,540
When I came home earlier,

888
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:58,700
I saw the clothes were dry.

889
00:40:58,700 --> 00:40:59,540
I got them off,

890
00:40:59,780 --> 00:41:01,380
