892
00:41:08,460 --> 00:41:09,780
Alright, I won't argue with you.

893
00:41:10,020 --> 00:41:11,060
Come here.

894
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:12,580
You don't need to do anything.

895
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:13,420
Did you add chili?

896
00:41:13,420 --> 00:41:14,660
Be a good girl, look pretty.

897
00:41:14,980 --> 00:41:16,090
- Sit here.
- Want some more oil?

898
00:41:16,090 --> 00:41:17,460
- Just wait for food.
- No need.

899
00:41:17,460 --> 00:41:18,540
- No, it’s fine.
- Almost done.

900
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:20,340
Freshly grilled meat.

901
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:21,340
Wait, wait a minute.

902
00:41:24,580 --> 00:41:25,420
Xia,

903
00:41:25,700 --> 00:41:26,900
this one has chili in it.

904
00:41:27,180 --> 00:41:28,100
She's got acnes recently.

905
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:29,380
On her back.

906
00:41:30,460 --> 00:41:32,900
Look at Cheng, he's so concerned about Yue.

907
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:34,660
I didn't even know

908
