I have acnes on my back.

909
00:41:35,980 --> 00:41:38,140
You just don't get as much care from your husband as you do.

910
00:41:38,140 --> 00:41:38,980
Not like him.

911
00:41:38,990 --> 00:41:40,900
If I get a bump on my forehead, he doesn't even notice.

912
00:41:41,500 --> 00:41:42,980
You'd look even more beautiful with a bump.

913
00:41:43,860 --> 00:41:44,700
Nonsense.

914
00:41:45,380 --> 00:41:46,220
Drink some tea.

915
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:48,740
Here, freshly made.

916
00:41:48,740 --> 00:41:49,580
No chili in this one.

917
00:41:49,860 --> 00:41:51,580
This one's good, you can eat it.

918
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:56,900
By the way, honey,

919
00:41:57,140 --> 00:41:58,260
When you have the time,

920
00:41:58,260 --> 00:42:00,580
I think you should take Xia with you to get a skin care.

921
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:02,020
Look at the results,

922
00:42:02,380 --> 00:42:03,300
so firm and tight.

923
00:42:05,060 --> 00:42:06,340
I'm not going any more.

924
00:42:09,380 --> 00:42:10,380
Why not?

925
00:42:13,140 --> 00:42:15,580
Zhou Wei, I've been hearing that someone from the company

926
00:42:15,820 --> 00:42:17,100
