927
00:42:17,100 --> 00:42:17,980
It has good reputation.

928
00:42:17,980 --> 00:42:19,260
Next time, we can try that place.

929
00:42:19,260 --> 00:42:20,420
I don't need it.

930
00:42:24,740 --> 00:42:26,020
Well,

931
00:42:26,020 --> 00:42:27,500
Yue is naturally beautiful.

932
00:42:30,300 --> 00:42:31,180
Okay, okay.

933
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:33,180
No need.

934
00:42:33,380 --> 00:42:34,540
No need to go.

935
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:37,620
Look at him.

936
00:42:38,020 --> 00:42:39,260
He values his wife's opinions.

937
00:42:40,180 --> 00:42:42,020
Zhou Wei's also really good to his wife.

938
00:42:42,660 --> 00:42:44,060
Compared to you, he's not worth mentioning.

939
00:42:44,180 --> 00:42:45,340
No one can compare to him.

940
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:47,260
He's famous for being a wife-doting husband.

941
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:49,380
You could learn a thing or two.

942
00:42:51,460 --> 00:42:52,900
Come on, the skewers are ready.

943
00:42:53,620 --> 00:42:54,540
They’re all done.

944
00:42:54,540 --> 00:42:55,380
Ziyuan, come on.

945
00:42:55,460 --> 00:42:56,300
All grilled.

946
00:42:56,860 --> 00:42:57,700
- Here you are.
- Share this

947
00:42:57,900 --> 00:42:58,740
