948
00:42:58,750 --> 00:43:00,000
(Everyone is envious.)

949
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:00,900
Be careful.

950
00:43:00,900 --> 00:43:02,500
(His love for me is so meticulous.)

951
00:43:03,580 --> 00:43:06,180
(But I'm only starting to feel more and more uncomfortable.)

952
00:43:06,780 --> 00:43:08,300
