953
00:43:09,220 --> 00:43:10,500
(a seemingly perfect world,)

954
00:43:11,140 --> 00:43:12,220
(a world I don't need to look at,)

955
00:43:12,660 --> 00:43:13,500
Don't be afraid,

956
00:43:13,780 --> 00:43:14,660
I'm here.

957
00:43:15,360 --> 00:43:16,380
(a world I don't need to listen to,)

958
00:43:16,940 --> 00:43:18,460
- (let alone to think about.)
- Come on.

959
00:43:19,660 --> 00:43:21,620
(I only need to follow his instructions.)

960
00:43:23,060 --> 00:43:23,980
(Go forward.)

961
00:43:25,140 --> 00:43:25,980
(Go back.)

962
00:43:27,700 --> 00:43:28,540
(Turn left.)

963
00:43:29,580 --> 00:43:30,420
(Turn right.)

964
00:43:31,540 --> 00:43:32,940
(And then tell myself,)

965
00:43:33,420 --> 00:43:34,860
(everything he's doing,)

966
00:43:35,410 --> 00:43:36,460
(is for me)

967
00:43:37,820 --> 00:43:39,020
(and for this family.)

968
00:43:40,580 --> 00:43:41,420
(But...)

969
00:43:42,340 --> 00:43:44,180
(When did it start?)

970
00:43:46,940 --> 00:43:49,140
I think Chinese women

971
00:43:49,490 --> 00:43:50,420
look elegant in a cheongsam.

972
00:43:50,900 --> 00:43:51,820
My wife doesn't drink.

973
00:43:52,300 --> 00:43:53,740
that the value you've created at home

974
00:43:53,740 --> 00:43:55,100
is no less than what I've contributed.

975
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:56,860
We can focus on getting ready to

976
00:43:57,100 --> 00:43:57,940
conceive.

977
00:43:58,020 --> 00:43:59,660
I only kept it from you

978
00:43:59,660 --> 00:44:01,020
