What can I say, my wife is really popular.

980
00:44:03,220 --> 00:44:04,980
She's not in a state to work right now.

981
00:44:05,940 --> 00:44:07,260
It's all my fault.

982
00:44:11,020 --> 00:44:12,580
We're husband and wife,

983
00:44:15,020 --> 00:44:16,860
No one knows her better than I do.

984
00:44:24,420 --> 00:44:26,500
(Is this the life I want?)

985
00:44:54,600 --> 00:44:56,240
♪When I got used to♪

986
